name: AESPA Winter
description:
Get v2 and v3 here .

Join KPOP Diffusion Discord: https://discord.gg/NrBDMX79Da

modelVersions.name: AESPA Winter - V1
modelVersions.description:
First 2023 Dreambooth version. Net 128. Trained on latest version of Linaqruf's colab using 30 images with HassanBlend 1.4 as its base model.

I use new settings for this, it's better in face similarity than the previous settings but it's harder to stylize it. Best at close-up, pose will be repetitive at some seeds and prompts because its dataset have many similar pose, but it can be solved with Controlnet, the face similarity will be decrease though.

If this is good enough for you all, I'll share guide and tutorial to making this, so let me know.
